data.description: Stop scrolling! This gorgeous home in a BRAND NEW neighborhood is NOT in a flood zone & has NO CDD! Get the upgrades that the builder isn’t including in this gently lived in Marsala Model. Welcome to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom executive home, nestled within a gated community. Built in 2021, this residence exudes elegance and offers an array of versatile spaces, including a den that can easily transform into an office, gym, or hobby room, catering to your every need.  As you step through the striking 3/4 glass front door, you're greeted by a large, bright foyer, setting the tone for the spaciousness that lies within. This premium lot location ensures both privacy and tranquility, providing a serene backdrop for your daily life.    The heart of this home is the oversized kitchen island, perfect for gathering and entertaining. A vast coffee bar adds a touch of luxury, making morning rituals a joy. Tile floors span the living areas, providing durability and easy maintenance, while plush carpets in the bedrooms offer comfort and warmth.    Every detail has been thoughtfully considered, with granite countertops gracing the kitchen and bathrooms, elevating the overall aesthetic. Professionally framed bathroom mirrors add a touch of sophistication and refinement.    Safety and security are paramount, as evidenced by the whole-house Ring alarm system and doorbell, ensuring peace of mind for you and your loved ones. Protection from the elements is seamlessly integrated, thanks to an in-wall pest control system and hurricane shutters for all openings.    The outdoors beckon with an oversized screened lanai, perfect for al fresco dining and relaxation. Inside, custom electric sheer zebra blinds allow natural light to filter in while preserving your privacy, striking a harmonious balance between openness and seclusion.    Within the community, you'll have access to an array of amenities, including a refreshing pool, pickleball courts, and a state-of-the-art gym, ensuring a lifestyle filled with leisure and recreation. On top of ALL that absolute AMAZINGNESS, the seller is offering a home warranty for your piece of mind!     This executive home is a testament to thoughtful design, quality craftsmanship, and modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and experience the epitome of upscale living in this quiet gated community.
